# ===== 密钥 / 凭证（绝对不能上传）=====
.env
**/.env
*.env
!*.env.example
**/.dy_cookie.txt
*cookie*.txt

# ===== 浏览器登录态 / 抓取数据（含会话，绝不上传）=====
**/browser_data/
**/data/
Spider_XHS/datas/

# ===== 运行产物（可再生，不传）=====
**/recruit_out/
**/dy_out/
recruit_out/
**/seen.json
**/progress.json
**/new_companies.json
**/master_seen.json

# ===== 依赖 / 虚拟环境 =====
**/node_modules/
node_modules/
**/.venv/
.venv/
venv/

# ===== Python =====
__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/

# ===== 临时文件 / 日志 =====
*.log
_*.md
.DS_Store

# ============================================================
# 第三方本体：整目录忽略，只保留“我自己写的文件”
